%A7/poem-1FwX65prJsA05uboQgeyRg">Thuỷ thượng quán thủ - 水上盥手</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-CZQp1s97hpqFaUs-3UnvYA">Cao Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-H%E1%BB%97/T%C3%ADch-t%C3%ADch-di%C3%AAm-Mi-vu-di%E1%BB%87p-ph%E1%BB%A5c-t%E1%BB%81/poem-CMgO4d9JnPFxSiFOyANBNA">Tích tích diêm - Mi vu diệp phục tề - 昔昔鹽－蘼蕪葉復齊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-H%E1%BB%97/author-ZK21rLayK3mmuHkvR5sQcg">Triệu Hỗ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vu-L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-S%E1%BB%AD/Xu%C3%A2n-s%C6%A1n-nguy%E1%BB%87t-d%E1%BA%A1/poem-KtSg_ffXkQoJWKSQaEu-rw">Xuân sơn nguyệt dạ - 春山夜月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vu-L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-S%E1%BB%AD/author-03JLqi_OZ6ZfUvagC1MyYg">Vu Lương Sử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-X%E1%BB%A9ng/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-K%C3%AA-L%C4%83ng-quan/poem-wYhX2y7qrhKOahg8PwhzzA">Xuất Kê Lăng quan - 出雞陵關</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-X%E1%BB%A9ng/author-vBlbyIvSq9KPD9Smt4LhVA">Vương Xứng</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
